text:
Good evening, Producer.
Do you have a moment right now?
Actually... I left something in the practice room.

Oh, really!
But, you know what we did earlier...?

Ghosts and such are unscientific, they can't possibly exist...!
They can't exist, but...

Well, it's dangerous to be alone at night, right!?
So, yeah!

Then, I'll walk ahead
so follow behind me.
Y-You don't have to go that far, you know?
